  <div class="block">
    <section class="hero is-primary">
      <div class="hero-body">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="title">Welcome to RuffHouse!</h1>
          <h2 class="subtitle">Welcome to <strong>RuffHouse</strong>, the home of your favorite furry friends. Woof!</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-image">
        <figure class="image is-4by3">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1108099/pexels-photo-1108099.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940" alt="Placeholder image">
        </figure>
      </div>
      <footer class="card-footer">
        <p class="card-footer-item">
          <span>
            <a href=""><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i>Twitter</a>
          </span>
        </p>
        <p class="card-footer-item">
          <span>
            <a href=""><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>Facebook</a>
          </span>
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="box is-justify-content-center">
    <h1 class="title">Product Overview</h1>
    <h2 class="subtitle">
      
    </h2>
    <div class="card-content">

<p>Your dog can benefit a lot from socializing with other dogs, but we know it can be hard finding a place for them to do that.</p>

<p>So we decided to build a web app that allows you to share a constant stream of dog pictures so you can share what your dog is upto and view posts by other users so you can start expanding your dog's community!</p>

    </div>
  </div>
  </section>


</section>
<div class="block">
  <h1 class="title">Our features include</h1>

  <div class="columns is-centered">
      <% features.forEach(function(feature){ %>
        <div class="column">
        <figure class="image is-256x256">
            <img src=<%= feature.img %> alt="Icon of a lock in 3D">
          <h2><%= feature.title %></h2>
        </figure>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    </div>

  </div>
<section class="section">
  <h1 class="title">Join our Community Today!</h1>
  <h2 class="section--title">What are you waiting for? Join our community of dogs and dog-lovers for FREE today!</h2>
  <a  class="button is-large shiny" href="#">Sign me up!</a>
</section>



